        <script type="application/ld&#x2B;json">
            {"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"SoftwareApplication","name":"Retrofy – Laai af en installeer op Windows | Microsoft Store","description":"Requires Microsoft .NET Desktop Runtime 8.0 x64. If it is not already installed, Windows may prompt you to install it before first launch.\n\nRetrofy is a retro image converter for Windows that transforms modern images using authentic classic hardware-style limitations instead of generic “vintage” filters.\n\nCreate images inspired by the visual rules of systems like the Nintendo Game Boy, NES, SNES, and Commodore 64. Retrofy applies constrained palettes, reduced color counts, retro-style resolution pressure, and era-appropriate image treatment so results feel closer to real old hardware aesthetics rather than a basic color overlay.\n\nWhether you want Game Boy-style monochrome looks, NES-style limited palette art, SNES-inspired 16-bit color treatment, or Commodore 64-style retro computer visuals, Retrofy gives you a fast desktop workflow for exploring and exporting nostalgic graphics.\n\nRetrofy is built for creators, pixel art fans, game developers, modders, thumbnail makers, stream asset designers, and anyone who wants to turn modern images into convincing retro-style artwork.\n\nIncluded retro-inspired targets:\n• Game Boy-style 4-shade handheld look\n• NES-style palette-limited console look\n• SNES-inspired 16-bit era color treatment\n• Commodore 64-style 16-color home computer look\n\nWhy Retrofy stands out:\n• Uses hardware-style visual limitations instead of generic retro presets\n• Fast preview workflow for trying multiple classic looks\n• Great for retro game art, social posts, thumbnails, wallpapers, and creative experiments\n• Clean desktop interface focused on load, preview, tweak, and export\n• Designed for people who want authentic retro vibes with less manual work\n\nIf you are looking for a retro image converter, pixel art filter, Game Boy filter, NES filter, SNES-style image effect, or Commodore 64 image style tool for Windows, Retrofy is built for exactly that workflow.","image":"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.49044.13666571791679282.7b35334f-47c1-47ca-a13a-73ac8ec7b958.f66aba71-23c3-4e87-b4e0-047e7589c9db","url":"https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9nk0mhg9f29r?hl=af-ZA&gl=ZA","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"BassThermal","url":"https://apps.microsoft.com/search/publisher?name=BassThermal&hl=af-ZA&gl=ZA"},"offers":{"@type":"Offer","price":"51","priceCurrency":"USD"},"applicationCategory":"Multimedia-ontwerp","applicationSubCategory":"Illustration & graphic design","featureList":["Convert images with authentic retro hardware-style visual limitations","Create Game Boy-inspired 4-shade handheld looks","Generate NES-style palette-limited retro graphics","Apply SNES-inspired 16-bit era image treatment","Create Commodore 64-style 16-color visuals","Preview retro transformations quickly in a focused desktop workflow","Export polished retro-styled images for art, thumbnails, posts, and creative projects","Built for creators, pixel art fans, game devs, and nostalgic design workflows"],"operatingSystem":"Windows 10 weergawe 17763.0 of hoër","screenshot":[{"BackgroundColor":"transparent","ForegroundColor":"","@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.43123.13666571791679282.7b35334f-47c1-47ca-a13a-73ac8ec7b958.e959cfaf-4699-4826-b6f5-c178141a58d7","position":"Desktop/0","height":1123,"width":1919},{"BackgroundColor":"transparent","ForegroundColor":"","@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.17953.13666571791679282.7b35334f-47c1-47ca-a13a-73ac8ec7b958.80327cc0-b9aa-4ce3-bba8-b6fe99fe0793","position":"Desktop/1","height":1113,"width":1919},{"BackgroundColor":"transparent","ForegroundColor":"","@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.54348.13666571791679282.7b35334f-47c1-47ca-a13a-73ac8ec7b958.12faf769-3d01-42d0-9f7b-e16897bd12da","position":"Desktop/2","height":1126,"width":1919},{"BackgroundColor":"transparent","ForegroundColor":"","@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.46718.13666571791679282.7b35334f-47c1-47ca-a13a-73ac8ec7b958.e6659dd4-e46a-447d-b4cd-a9d824511b44","position":"Desktop/3","height":1121,"width":1919},{"BackgroundColor":"transparent","ForegroundColor":"","@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.45599.13666571791679282.f201d28f-5ec6-4773-82ac-bf8efe50eb98.cf79ce53-cf39-47e8-80b0-d02a48a20d31","position":"Desktop/4","height":1129,"width":1918},{"BackgroundColor":"transparent","ForegroundColor":"","@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.38745.13666571791679282.f201d28f-5ec6-4773-82ac-bf8efe50eb98.d39b4ca6-037a-45c4-aae6-633ef7e860a7","position":"Desktop/5","height":1129,"width":1919}]}
        </script>

